        "text_ectxRp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>ASPA-Fernblock® is the latest evolution in skin photoprotection - a next-generation patented bioactive complex designed to enhance the protective benefits of HELIOCARE while supporting skin health beyond UV protection.</p><p>This innovative technology combines two powerful plant-based actives: Fernblock®+, Cantabria Labs' patented <em>Polypodium leucotomos</em> extract with clinically proven antioxidant and photoprotective properties, and ASPA, a patented extract derived from <em>Aspalathus linearis</em> (Rooibos), a plant naturally rich in flavonoids with recognised biological activity. Together, they create ASPA-Fernblock®, an additive complex exclusive to Cantabria Labs products.<br/><br/>ASPA-Fernblock® has been shown to enhance the efficacy of UV filters, supporting more comprehensive protection across the full spectrum of solar radiation, including UVA, UVB, visible light and infrared-A. It also delivers the OptiD Effect, helping to preserve vitamin D receptors under oxidative stress and supporting the skin's ability to utilise vitamin D more effectivtly.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
