    "rich_text_NBTVdd": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_D8PdbV": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Oral Fernblock® & Supporting High-Risk Patients",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_aeaRnm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>HELIOCARE's oral supplement range provides photoprotection support using patented Fernblock® (<em>Polypodium leucotomos</em>) extract, developed as an adjuvant to topical sunscreen in patients where photoprotection is clinically critical. The clinical literature supports oral Fernblock® as an adjuvant in dermatological pathways linked to UV and visible light exposure, including: </p>"
          }
        }
      },
